title: Wallace trade, Tebow workout, Lindsay Rhodes
itunes:title: Wallace trade, Tebow workout, Lindsay Rhodes
description:
A room filled with some heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler -- continues its analysis of free agency, picking apart all the biggest news stories around the league. With NFL Media's Lindsay Rhodes in studio, the gang takes a look at Mike Wallace's trade to the Minnnesota Vikings, Tim Tebow's workout in The City of Brotherly Love and much, much more.
